      "created_at": "2024-05-28T07:42:07.697Z",
      "cooked": "<p>You are extremely good at this <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\">   You seem like a good/great product manager or UX designer <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\"> \u2026</p>\n<p>We have this now if you are using my plans.  I assume you mean something like this when using the calendar.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2_2_311x499.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"wm5dZKHBfhvqhkSVppwYlLx7iFQ\" width=\"311\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2_2_311x499.jpeg, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2_2_466x748.jpeg 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2_2_622x998.jpeg 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/e/e2c4a602a59d468f7be7ed5045345b0c8fe2cea2_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1006\u00d71614 192 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Also the TODAY tab shows today\u2019s workout.  Why is that not enough?</p>",
